---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="关于">
  <section class="surface about stack" data-reveal>
    <p class="section-kicker">About</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">关于我</h1>
    <p class="muted">
      随手做的纯前端静态博客。
    </p>

    <div class="stack feature-list">
      <h2>所以这个站有什么？</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Astro 静态生成，Markdown 驱动内容。</li>
        <li>固定暗黑模式 + 绿色主题设计系统。</li>
        <li>Shiki 构建期代码高亮，移动端可滚动代码块。</li>
        <li>内置标签、归档、RSS、Sitemap 和 GitHub Pages 发布流程。</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 1.3rem;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.18rem;
    font-family: "Space Grotesk", "IBM Plex Sans", sans-serif;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.15rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.48rem;
  }

  .feature-list {
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }
</style>
